crowdsourced_ai_results.analysis:
The malware establishes persistence by modifying the 'HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Command Processor\AutoRun' registry key. It then uses the dynamically resolved 'WinExec' API to execute 'mshta.exe' to download and run a remote HTML Application (HTA) file. This is characteristic of a downloader or dropper.

IOCs:
- URL: http://ksi/1.hta
- Registry Key: HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Command Processor /v AutoRun
